**Internal Communication**
* Establish internal communication strategies to ensure organizational initiatives and projects are successfully and consistently communicated to employees and stakeholders;
* Develop and implement employee engagement programs;
* Handle the internal communications responses to crisis situations that affect organizational perception and reputation;
* Create ongoing and innovative engagement programs to continuously evolve our employer brand.



**Employer Branding**
